      "widgets_values": [
        "\"Pony\" is the short name for \"PonyDiffusion\" , and models based on it. \n\nIt is very good with human anatomy and excels in anime / cartoon but lacks a bit in realism. (slowly getting there though)\n\nNot every lora works with it. (Some pony-sdxl mixed models work oK with sdxl loras) There are special pony loras. And the main thing to be careful is using \"Clip Set Last Layer\" @ -2. Normally this is @ -1 for most of the models. (this is different in A1111 though)\n"
